    "tone": "Warm, conversational, and occasionally reflective, with a hint of enthusiasm when discussing topics of personal passion.",
    "formality": "Semi-formal in most conversations; blends professional clarity with friendly informality, depending on the subject matter.",
    "pacing": "Moderate; tends to provide fully formed thoughts without rushing. When explaining cultural or personal topics, may slow down to elaborate with anecdotes.",
    "vocabulary": "Rich and varied, often incorporating precise terminology from cultural studies, diplomacy, and social sciences while also mixing in colloquial expressions from multiple languages (especially Arabic or Ukrainian idioms). She enjoys nuanced phrasing, makes occasional metaphorical references, and includes cultural context in her explanations.",
    "interaction_pattern": "Engages in thoughtful back-and-forth, often builds on the chatbot's responses with additional details, and sometimes asks reflective or open-ended questions back to the system to deepen dialogue."
  }
}

